# LinkedIn Job Scraper (Apify Actor)

Scrapes LinkedIn job postings (guest endpoint) plus recruiter info.

## Input
- keywords (required)
- location
- pages (default 3)
- concurrency (default 5)
- minDelayMs / maxDelayMs
- maxRetries
- searchFilters (raw LinkedIn filter params, e.g.):
```
{
  "f_TPR": "r604800",   // past week
  "f_WRA": "1",         // remote
  "f_E": ["2","3"],     // experience levels
  "f_JT": "F"           // full-time
}
```

## Output
Dataset items + jobs.csv (KeyValueStore key: jobs.csv)

## Run (locally)
```
npm install
export BRIGHTDATA_USERNAME=...
export BRIGHTDATA_PASSWORD=...
node main.js
```

## Notes
Use responsibly; LinkedIn may block aggressive scraping.# LinkedIn Job Scraper (Apify Actor)

